These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, water, coffee
1. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | water | coffee | fanta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, mango, radish
1. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Food   | watermelon | mango | radish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff, dunhill
1. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Cigar   | game | davidoff | dunhill |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
