.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, romance, drama
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | satire | drama |

